Helen Trix https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Trix 0 Helen Trix (1886 – November 19, 1951) was an American actress, dancer, singer, and song composer. The August 1906 edition of Edison Phonograph Monthly describes her as having a "clear, well modulated contralto voice".
